<!-- ====== BENEFITS ====== -->
<section class="benefits-section" id="benefits">
    <div class="section-watermark" style="top: 60px; right: -30px;">+</div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header centered reveal">
            <div class="section-eyebrow">+ &nbsp;Why DealGrowth</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">The <em>Advantage</em></h2>
            <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top: 16px;">What you gain when you stop scaling through headcount.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="benefits-grid">
            <div class="benefit-card reveal">
                <div class="benefit-icon">&#128640;</div>
                <div class="benefit-title">24/7 Pipeline Generation</div>
                <div class="benefit-desc">AI never sleeps, never takes vacation, and never misses a follow-up. Your pipeline fills itself.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-card reveal reveal-d1">
                <div class="benefit-icon">&#128200;</div>
                <div class="benefit-title">Infinite Personalization</div>
                <div class="benefit-desc">Every message tailored to the prospect's role, company, and intent signals at a scale no human team can match.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-card reveal reveal-d2">
                <div class="benefit-icon">&#9889;</div>
                <div class="benefit-title">Zero Learning Curve</div>
                <div class="benefit-desc">No hiring, no training, no ramp time. Systems are live and producing within weeks, not quarters.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-card reveal">
                <div class="benefit-icon">&#128273;</div>
                <div class="benefit-title">Full Stack Integration</div>
                <div class="benefit-desc">Native connections to your existing CRM, email, calendar, and communication tools. No migration required.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-card reveal reveal-d1">
                <div class="benefit-icon">&#127919;</div>
                <div class="benefit-title">Data-Driven Optimization</div>
                <div class="benefit-desc">Every interaction is tracked, measured, and optimized. The system learns what works and doubles down.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-card reveal reveal-d2">
                <div class="benefit-icon">&#128176;</div>
                <div class="benefit-title">Fraction of the Cost</div>
                <div class="benefit-desc">Replace an entire SDR team for less than the salary of one rep. Clear ROI from month one.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ====== CASE STUDIES ====== -->
<section class="cases-section" id="cases">
    <div class="section-watermark" style="top: 100px; right: -60px;">03</div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header centered reveal">
            <div class="section-eyebrow">03 &nbsp;Selected Work</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Real <em>Outcomes</em></h2>
            <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top: 16px;">A cross-section of recent engagements across venture capital, health tech, manufacturing, and political campaigns.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cases-grid">
        <div class="case-card reveal">
            <div class="case-card-header"><div class="case-logo-initial">AV</div><div class="case-industry">Venture Capital</div></div>
            <div class="case-company">Avalanche Capital</div>
            <div class="case-quote">"From zero LP conversations to our first $500K closed check in under eight weeks. The velocity was unlike anything we'd experienced."</div>
            <a href="#" class="case-link">View Case Study &rarr;</a>
            <div class="case-metrics"><div><div class="case-metric-v">$2.4M</div><div class="case-metric-l">New AUM</div></div><div><div class="case-metric-v">8 wks</div><div class="case-metric-l">To Close</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card reveal reveal-d1">
            <div class="case-card-header"><div class="case-logo-initial">NX</div><div class="case-industry">HealthTech</div></div>
            <div class="case-company">NXAI Health</div>
            <div class="case-quote">"We replaced our demand gen function entirely. More demos, higher quality, and at a fraction of the headcount cost."</div>
            <a href="#" class="case-link">View Case Study &rarr;</a>
            <div class="case-metrics"><div><div class="case-metric-v">+890%</div><div class="case-metric-l">Demo Requests</div></div><div><div class="case-metric-v">63%</div><div class="case-metric-l">Cost Cut</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card reveal reveal-d2">
            <div class="case-card-header"><div class="case-logo-initial">BN</div><div class="case-industry">Manufacturing</div></div>
            <div class="case-company">Bellini's Newry</div>
            <div class="case-quote">"Traditional outreach was dead for us. DealGrowth opened doors we didn't know existed. The pipeline is unrecognizable."</div>
            <a href="#" class="case-link">View Case Study &rarr;</a>
            <div class="case-metrics"><div><div class="case-metric-v">$1.1M</div><div class="case-metric-l">New Contracts</div></div><div><div class="case-metric-v">4&times;</div><div class="case-metric-l">Pipeline Volume</div></div></div>
